                    <p style="font-size: 1.1em; font-weight: 600; color: #667eea;">AI is analyzing your product...</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #999; margin-top: 10px;">This usually takes 10-20 seconds</p>
                </div>
                
